## 주요 스키마 요약 (프론트엔드에서 자주 참조할 필드)

- **LocationListResponse**
  - **total**: integer — 전체 개수 (required)
  - **page**: integer — 현재 페이지 (required)
  - **size**: integer — 페이지 사이즈 (required)
  - **items**: `LocationSummary[]` (required)

- **LocationSummary**
  - **id**: integer (required)
  - **content_id**: string (required)
  - **title**: string (required)
  - **region**: string|null
  - **addr1**: string|null
  - **firstimage**: string|null
  - **cat1**: string|null
  - **water_rocket_index**: number (required)
  - **pre_visit_avg**: number (required)
  - **post_visit_avg**: number (required)

- **LocationDetail**
  - 위 Summary 필드 포함 및 추가:
  - **addr2**, **zipcode**, **tel**, **mapx**, **mapy**, **areacode**, **sigungucode**, **cat2**, **cat3**, **firstimage2**
  - **pre_visit_count**, **post_visit_count**, **comment_count**: integer (기본값 0)
  - **required**: `id`, `content_id`, `title`, `water_rocket_index`, `pre_visit_avg`, `post_visit_avg`

- **PreVisitEvaluationCreate**
  - **author**: string, 1~50 (required)
  - **expectation_score**: integer (1..5) (required)

- **PreVisitEvaluationOut**
  - **id**, **location_id**, **author**, **expectation_score**, **created_at** (required)

- **PostVisitEvaluationCreate**
  - **author**: string, 1~50 (required)
  - **satisfaction_score**: integer (1..5) (required)
  - **revisit_intention**: boolean|null
  - **visited_at**: date|null

- **PostVisitEvaluationOut**
  - **id**, **location_id**, **author**, **satisfaction_score**, **revisit_intention**, **visited_at**, **created_at** (required 일부 있음)

- **CommentCreate**
  - **author**: string, 1~50 (required)
  - **content**: string, 1~2000 (required)
  - **password**: string, pattern `^\d{4}$` (4자리 숫자, required)

- **CommentDelete**
  - **password**: string, pattern `^\d{4}$` (required)

- **CommentOut**
  - **id**, **location_id**, **author**, **content**, **created_at**, **updated_at** (updated_at은 null 허용)

- **WaterRocketExtremesResponse**
  - **highest**: `LocationSummary[]` (required)
  - **lowest**: `LocationSummary[]` (required)

- **WaterRocketIndexOut**
  - **location_id**: integer (required)
  - **pre_visit_avg**: number (required)
  - **post_visit_avg**: number (required)
  - **water_rocket_index**: number (required)

- **ValidationError**
  - **loc**: (string|integer)[] — 에러 위치
  - **msg**: string — 에러 메시지
  - **type**: string — 에러 타입

- **HTTPValidationError**
  - **detail**: `ValidationError[]`

